我也是这么干的 我摧毁了许多海盗船
And that's what I did, I destroyed dozens of ships.

699
01:01:58,010 --> 01:02:02,140
最后剩下的那些 集合起来 妄图打败我
The last ones joined together to try and defeat me.

700
01:02:02,640 --> 01:02:05,230
但不久 他们也意识到 毫无希望
But they soon realized it was hopeless.

701
01:02:16,910 --> 01:02:19,530
没人能阻挡沉默玛丽号
Nothing could stop the Silent Mary.

702
01:02:20,580 --> 01:02:22,370
在水面以下攻击
Hit them below the water line.

703
01:02:22,450 --> 01:02:23,620
快 快
Vamo, vamo!

704
01:02:26,670 --> 01:02:29,000
坚持住
Hang on tight!

705
01:02:37,640 --> 01:02:41,220
海洋终于 纯净了
The sea was finally... pure.

706
01:02:42,140 --> 01:02:45,690
卑鄙的海盗船不会再玷污海洋
Their wretched flags will no longer stain the sea.

707
01:02:54,240 --> 01:02:55,820
他们在祈求饶恕
They are begging for mercy.

708
01:02:57,030 --> 01:03:00,300
怜悯？
Mercy?

709
01:03:01,120 --> 01:03:02,540
绝不姑息
There's no mercy.

710
01:03:08,790 --> 01:03:10,000
准备好
Make ready.

711
01:03:16,590 --> 01:03:18,720
- 再见了！ - 开火！
- Adios! - Fire!

712
01:03:27,850 --> 01:03:30,060
现在就看你了 杰克
It's up to you now Jack.

713
01:03:32,190 --> 01:03:36,360
这个罗盘 指向你最想要的
This compass... points towards what you want most.

714
01:03:38,490 --> 01:03:41,370
永远不要背叛它
Never betray it.

715
01:04:12,520 --> 01:04:14,860
魔鬼三角洲
The Devil's Triangle.

716
01:04:16,230 --> 01:04:20,910
他们最后的海盗船 在我眼前燃烧
The last of their ships were burning before my eyes.

717
01:04:22,450 --> 01:04:26,580
就在 胜利时刻
And in that moment of... Victori.

718
01:04:27,040 --> 01:04:28,830
就在那时 我听到了
It's when I heard it.

719
01:04:30,540 --> 01:04:32,670
等一等 船长
Hold on, Captain.

720
01:04:33,000 --> 01:04:36,170
有一条船想冲出烟雾逃跑
One ship was trying to escape through the smoke.

721
01:04:36,340 --> 01:04:38,760
出海的好日子 对吧
It's a lovely day for a sail, ain't it?

722
01:04:38,970 --> 01:04:40,090
就在那里
And there.

723
01:04:40,550 --> 01:04:45,480
在瞭望台 就是那个年轻的海盗
In the crow's nest, there was this young pirate boy.

724
01:04:45,560 --> 01:04:47,850
在我看来 就只有我们两个了
The way I see it, it just the two of us left.

725
01:04:48,640 --> 01:04:51,060
你要是现在投降 我就让你活 简单极了
If you surrender to me now, I'll let you live, simple.

726
01:04:51,140 --> 01:04:54,440
他站在那里 就像 一只小鸟
He stood there, looking like. A little bird...

727
01:04:55,320 --> 01:04:58,030
那天之后 他赢得了那个
And from that day he earned himself a name that would...

728
01:04:58,230 --> 01:05:00,570
纠缠我一辈子的名字
haunt me for the rest of my days.

729
01:05:02,450 --> 01:05:03,820
杰克·斯派洛
Jack de "Sparrow".

730
01:05:04,280 --> 01:05:08,080
好啦 你现在投降 我就让你活
Right, you surrender to me now, and I'll let you live.

731
01:05:09,410 --> 01:05:11,620
我可以让你活下来
I shall let you live.

732
01:05:17,800 --> 01:05:19,090
这个男孩
This boy.

733
01:05:19,340 --> 01:05:21,640
这个男孩居然嘲笑我的力量
This boy was mocking my power.

734
01:05:21,720 --> 01:05:24,810
所以我就追上去 打定主意
So I test him. Knowing that I would run...

735
01:05:24,890 --> 01:05:29,560
要让我的刀已经划过他的脖子 当他死了 我就终于能...
My knife along his neck, and when he was dead, I would finish finally...

736
01:05:29,640 --> 01:05:31,180
终结了所有的海盗
With pirates's life.

737
01:05:36,230 --> 01:05:37,360
追上去
Follow him men!

738
01:05:38,690 --> 01:05:41,280
大炮都推过来 拿一些缆绳
To the gutholes. Thread some lines.

739
01:05:43,700 --> 01:05:45,240
准备急转
Prepare the boot leg!

740
01:05:45,370 --> 01:05:46,410
左舷
Port side.

741
01:05:48,620 --> 01:05:49,740
扔下去
Throw it now.

742
01:06:11,930 --> 01:06:13,060
他们掉头了
They're turning around.

743
01:07:22,880 --> 01:07:24,050
这都是什么
What's all this?

744
01:07:27,550 --> 01:07:30,050
贡品 先生
Tribute... Sir.

745
01:07:59,960 --> 01:08:01,790
他夺走了我的一切
He took everything from me.

746
01:08:02,540 --> 01:08:05,550
让我充满 狂怒
And filled me with... rage.

747
01:08:08,300 --> 01:08:09,590
和痛苦
And pain.

748
01:08:11,590 --> 01:08:14,100
他就是传说的终结
And he is where the tale ends.

749
01:08:16,680 --> 01:08:18,600
还没呢 船长 那里
Not yet Capitan, there.

750
01:08:19,520 --> 01:08:21,230
我就说会找到的
Found as promised.

751
01:08:45,630 --> 01:08:47,340
她说自己有地图
So she's saying she's got the map,

752
01:08:47,420 --> 01:08:48,890
但是她是唯一能看懂的
but she's the only one who can follow it?

753
01:08:48,970 --> 01:08:51,350
- 所以我们要 - 别管她
- So we should...? - Leave her be.

754
01:08:51,430 --> 01:08:54,020
- 她会带我们到三叉戟 - 你都说了几个小时了
- She will take us to the Trident. - You've been saying that for hours.

755
01:08:54,100 --> 01:08:57,640
我们可以确信的有两件事 白天没有星星
Two things we know are true, the stars don't shine by day.

756
01:08:57,810 --> 01:08:59,560
还有 她忘了带驴子
And she forgot a donkey.

757
01:08:59,980 --> 01:09:04,110
那我们怎么去一个地图上找不到的地方
How can we go to a spot, where no land exists on any map?

758
01:09:05,690 --> 01:09:08,360
这个航海经线仪跟伦敦时间一模一样
This chronometer keeps the exact time in London.

759
01:09:08,690 --> 01:09:10,370
我用它做海拔测量
I'm using it to make an altitude measurement...

760
01:09:10,450 --> 01:09:11,950
来确定经度
To determine longitude.

761
01:09:12,530 --> 01:09:15,000
只有这样 我们才能找到确切的观测点
Only then will we find our exact spot to see.

762
01:09:15,080 --> 01:09:17,620
所以你是打算用一个表来找到三叉戟
So you expect to find the trident with a timepiece?

763
01:09:17,700 --> 01:09:18,750
对的
Yes.

764
01:09:19,500 --> 01:09:21,580
我的计算十分准确
My calculations are precise and true.

765
01:09:21,870 --> 01:09:23,210
我不光是天文学家
I'm not only an Astronomer.

766
01:09:23,290 --> 01:09:24,790
我也是个钟表专家
I am also a horologist.

767
01:09:30,260 --> 01:09:31,630
没什么丢人的
No shame in that dear.

768
01:09:31,880 --> 01:09:35,100
大家都要糊口嘛
We'll all have to earn a living, eh?

769
01:09:36,680 --> 01:09:39,560
不 我说我是钟表专家
No, I'm a horologist.

770
01:09:39,640 --> 01:09:42,600
我妈也是啊 她也没有像你这样大声宣布
So was my mum. But she didn't cry a bad as lad as you.

771
01:09:42,810 --> 01:09:45,150
你的意思是你妈也有一定学术研究背景吗
You saying your mother was academically inclined?

772
01:09:45,230 --> 01:09:49,650
不如说 平躺着的背景吧
More like a horizontally, reclined.

773
01:09:50,650 --> 01:09:52,950
钟表学是研究时间的
Horology is the study of time.

774
01:09:53,030 --> 01:09:55,200
她也总在看时间啊
And she was always looking at watch.

775
01:09:55,450 --> 01:09:56,660
这点我敢保证
I can vouch for that.

776
01:09:58,490 --> 01:10:01,960
所以 只有你能找到宝藏 是么
So no one can find the X, but you, right?

777
01:10:02,250 --> 01:10:02,830
不
No.

778
01:10:02,910 --> 01:10:05,170
- 还有驴子吗 - 后方有船
- And the donkey? - Ship to the f!

779
01:10:07,710 --> 01:10:08,710
萨拉查
Salazar.

780
01:10:13,010 --> 01:10:15,600
杰克 亡灵在得到复仇之前是不会停下的
Jack, the dead will not rest until they get their revenge.

781
01:10:15,680 --> 01:10:16,640
亡灵
Dead?

782
01:10:16,720 --> 01:10:17,560
不 不 亡灵
No, no, the dead.

783
01:10:17,640 --> 01:10:20,270
- 你没说有亡灵的事情 - 就不应该来
- Were never part of this deal. - We should've never follow.

784
01:10:20,350 --> 01:10:22,520
跟着一个倒霉船长和女巫出海
A luck less pirate and a witch to sea.

785
01:10:22,600 --> 01:10:24,390
不管了 把他们都杀了
Right, that's it. Kill them all.

786
01:10:25,310 --> 01:10:28,270
杀了我 然后 然后我就死了
Kill me and, and... I will be dead.

787
01:10:28,770 --> 01:10:32,780
那些亡灵就没法复仇了
And then the other dead won't be able to have the revenge.

788
01:10:33,780 --> 01:10:35,160
对我复仇
Against me,

789
01:10:35,410 --> 01:10:36,990
- 我就死了 - 什么
- I'd be dead. - What?

790
01:10:37,070 --> 01:10:38,950
- 他们将会更加愤怒 - 他说得对
- Which will anger them even more. - He's right.

791
01:10:39,030 --> 01:10:39,780
说得对
That's right.

792
01:10:39,950 --> 01:10:41,710
海盗都这么没脑子么
Are all pirates this stupid?

793
01:10:41,790 --> 01:10:43,790
对的
Yes.

794
01:10:43,870 --> 01:10:45,500
那我们怎么办呢
What are we going to do?

795
01:10:46,290 --> 01:10:47,460
作为船长
As Captain.

796
01:10:48,750 --> 01:10:50,340
我能建议下么
Might I suggest.

797
01:10:54,920 --> 01:10:56,970
兵变 你非得建议兵变
Mutiny? You had to suggest a mutiny?

798
01:10:57,050 --> 01:10:58,550
卡丽娜 亡灵就要来了
Carina, the dead are coming.

799
01:10:58,640 --> 01:11:01,980
反正 我是不相信什么超自然的屁话
Well. I choose not to believe in supernatural nonsense.

800
01:11:02,060 --> 01:11:03,730
你难道没看到我们身后是什么
Do you not see what's behind us?

801
01:11:17,700 --> 01:11:19,490
- 把它们放下去 - 遵命
- Drop them! - Si.

802
01:11:19,570 --> 01:11:20,830
放下去
Drop them!

803
01:11:28,000 --> 01:11:28,840
你干什么
What are you doing?

804
01:11:28,920 --> 01:11:30,380
船上的那些人在找杰克
Men on that ship are looking for Jack.

805
01:11:30,460 --> 01:11:31,670
杰克在这条小船上
And Jack is on this boat.

806
01:11:31,750 --> 01:11:32,960
我还是逃跑吧
I'm going to swim for it.

807
01:11:33,050 --> 01:11:35,880
你怎么敢学我
How dare you do exactly what I'd do if I were you?

808
01:11:36,010 --> 01:11:38,590
- 卡丽娜 别这样 - 不 不 不 千万别停
- Carina stop! - No, no, no, don't stop.

809
01:11:38,840 --> 01:11:41,100
- 你够了 - 够什么够
- This has gone far enough. - No, it has not.

810
01:11:41,640 --> 01:11:44,560
别听他的 接着脱 接着脱！
Listen not to him, carry on, carry on!

811
01:11:50,860 --> 01:11:54,230
- 干嘛 眼看着要脱光了 - 我看到她的脚踝了
- Why, she was almost finished. - I saw her ankles.

812
01:11:54,320 --> 01:11:56,860
你个傻小子要是闭嘴还能看到更多呢
You'd have to seen a lot more, if you kept the cakeholes shut.

813
01:12:15,000 --> 01:12:16,670
去杀了斯派洛
Kill the sparrow.

814
01:12:33,520 --> 01:12:35,320
这可不妙
That's not good, is it?

815
01:12:36,150 --> 01:12:39,000
接着划 伙计 再快点！
Keep rowing man. Faster!

816
01:12:39,300 --> 01:12:40,860
不 受够鸟
No, that's it.

817
01:12:41,990 --> 01:12:43,320
我去找她了
I'm going with her.

818
01:12:44,160 --> 01:12:47,420
你为了个光穿内衣的钟表专家就要抛弃我？
You would leave me for some horologist in her knickers?

819
01:12:47,500 --> 01:12:48,500
没错
Yes.

820
01:12:50,000 --> 01:12:51,670
臭男人都一个样
You men are all alike.

821
01:13:01,840 --> 01:13:02,840
鲨鱼
Shark.

822
01:13:27,910 --> 01:13:29,000
亨利！
Henry!

823
01:13:51,350 --> 01:13:52,650
看来没用
Doesn't seem to be working.

824
01:13:52,730 --> 01:13:54,850
不 没事儿 没事儿的
No, we'll be fine, we'll be fine.

825
01:14:14,670 --> 01:14:16,750
- 这是怎么搞的 - 我们必须游泳了
- How did they do that? - We have to swim.

826
01:14:16,960 --> 01:14:19,090
我来引开他
I will distract him.

827
01:14:24,590 --> 01:14:25,590
就现在
Now!

828
01:15:06,220 --> 01:15:07,890
亨利
Henry!

829
01:15:58,560 --> 01:16:01,360
嗨 杰克·斯派洛
Hi... Jack Sparrow.

830
01:16:03,400 --> 01:16:05,070
杰克·斯派洛
Jack Sparrow.

831
01:16:05,150 --> 01:16:06,240
西班牙人
Spanish?

832
01:16:13,870 --> 01:16:15,410
鬼魂
Ghosts.

833
01:16:16,200 --> 01:16:18,290
他们无法登陆
They are unable to step on land.

834
01:16:19,040 --> 01:16:20,920
- 我就知道 - 有鬼啊！
- I knew that. - Ghosts!

835
01:16:24,710 --> 01:16:28,010
- 卡丽娜 - 你很快就会为自己所做的付出代价
- Carina! - You will soon pay for what you did to me.

836
01:16:28,090 --> 01:16:30,470
不 不 不 真心不用麻烦了
No no no. There is no need to bother really.

837
01:16:30,550 --> 01:16:32,220
- 卡丽娜 - 没空跟你聊
- Carina! - I have no time to chat.

838
01:16:32,300 --> 01:16:36,100
- 因为我的地图要跑了 - 那我等着你
- Because mi map just ran away. - I'll be waiting for you.

839
01:16:36,640 --> 01:16:39,690
等我干嘛 他为什么非要等我
Why would you be waiting for me? Why would he be waiting for me?

840
01:16:56,490 --> 01:16:57,660
有海盗
Pirates!

841
01:17:12,430 --> 01:17:13,430
史考姆
Scrum.

842
01:17:13,890 --> 01:17:14,760
船长
Captain?

843
01:17:14,850 --> 01:17:17,310
杰克说 如果他有什么意外
Jack always told me that if anything should ever happened to him.

844
01:17:17,390 --> 01:17:21,310
- 他要你当船长 - 但是大家支持你
- He wanted you to be captain. - Yes, but the men voted for you, yes?

845
01:17:21,390 --> 01:17:22,820
所以 你得到了船长的帽子
Well, you've got a captain's hat!

846
01:17:22,900 --> 01:17:25,190
尽管如此 那是杰克的遗愿呢
"Be that as it may" them were his wishes.

847
01:17:25,270 --> 01:17:27,400
所以听话 去掌舵吧
So be a good lad and take the wheel.

848
01:17:27,480 --> 01:17:28,610
还有你
And... you,

849
01:17:29,820 --> 01:17:35,120
- 帽子归你了 - 哎呀妈呀 好荣幸
- Take the captain's hat. - Perish my rhythm.

850
01:17:38,160 --> 01:17:39,870
我们要揍死你们的船长
We will beat your captain to death.

851
01:17:39,950 --> 01:17:41,920
除非他告诉我们他们去哪里了
Until he reveals where they are heading.

852
01:17:44,460 --> 01:17:47,670
- 卡丽娜 - 我知道你纠结的是什么
- Carina! - I know what's ailing you boy.

853
01:17:47,750 --> 01:17:49,880
你有个地方痒痒但是挠不到
You've got the unstretchable itch.

854
01:17:50,220 --> 01:17:52,840
卡丽娜是唯一能带我们找到三叉戟的人
Carina is the only one who can help us find the Trident.

855
01:17:52,970 --> 01:17:55,140
- 我才没有爱上她 - 爱？
- And I'm not in love with her. - Love?

856
01:17:55,430 --> 01:17:57,430
谁说你爱了 你说什么呢？
Who said anything about love, what are you talking about?

857
01:17:57,510 --> 01:17:58,560
挠不到的痒痒
The unstretchable itch.

858
01:17:58,890 --> 01:18:00,940
疥疮 我说的是疥疮
Scabies, I'm talking about scabies.

859
01:18:01,020 --> 01:18:03,270
皮肤下面的钻来钻去小虫子
Small mites that burrow under the skin.

860
01:18:03,520 --> 01:18:05,480
烦死我了 都好几年了
Certainly annoying me, has done for years.

861
01:18:05,560 --> 01:18:06,650
糟糕
Oh, no!

862
01:18:09,360 --> 01:18:10,530
救命
Help!

863
01:18:11,530 --> 01:18:13,910
- 救救我 救命 - 卡丽娜
- Help me! Help! - Carina!

864
01:18:14,990 --> 01:18:17,530
- 亨利 帮帮我 - 快帮她
- Henry, help me. - Help her!

865
01:18:19,040 --> 01:18:20,460
奉天承运 国王诏曰
By rule of the King.

866
01:18:20,540 --> 01:18:22,620
你们全被判处死刑
I sentence you all to death.

867
01:18:23,420 --> 01:18:27,920
我们应该透露下彼此的私房钱藏哪里了
I think we should tell each other where our treasures are buried...

868
01:18:28,000 --> 01:18:29,970
万一谁幸存了可以交给他
Just in case one of us survives.

869
