好主意
Oh, good idea.

871
01:18:31,800 --> 01:18:34,930
- 你先说 - 我的宝藏被埋在
- You go first. - My treasure is buried...

872
01:18:35,010 --> 01:18:37,430
阿鲁巴岛上两颗交叉的棕榈树下为标记的墓地
Between two cross palm trees in an unmarked grave in Aruba.

873
01:18:37,510 --> 01:18:39,850
你的宝藏呢
What about yours?

874
01:18:41,020 --> 01:18:42,350
我没有宝藏
I haven't got any.

875
01:18:42,430 --> 01:18:44,110
你答应我杀死杰克的
You promised me Jack's blood.

876
01:18:44,190 --> 01:18:45,560
但杰克被困住了
But Jack is trapped!

877
01:18:46,020 --> 01:18:49,320
- 他永远逃不出去了 - 再小也是陆地！
- He can never escape the island. - Piece of land!

878
01:18:55,570 --> 01:18:56,570
你们好
Hello.

879
01:19:01,080 --> 01:19:02,660
我遵守了约定
I upheld our deal.

880
01:19:02,790 --> 01:19:04,580
我和手下会上岸去
Mi men and myself will go ashore.

881
01:19:04,750 --> 01:19:06,830
我会把叛徒交还给你
The traitor will be yours.

882
01:19:07,170 --> 01:19:09,090
- 以我的名誉发誓 - 名誉
- On mi honor. - Honor?

883
01:19:09,670 --> 01:19:11,670
你这个家伙有何名誉可言
What honor, hombre? What honor?

884
01:19:11,800 --> 01:19:14,380
- 你根本不懂名誉 - 请绕我一命
- You don't know what the honor is. - Spare mi my life.

885
01:19:14,720 --> 01:19:17,050
我会把你要的小矮子斯派洛带来
And I'll fetch you little Sparrow.

886
01:19:19,430 --> 01:19:20,810
同意吗
An accord?

887
01:19:35,070 --> 01:19:38,620
醒醒 斯派洛
Wake up Sparrow.

888
01:19:41,950 --> 01:19:44,700
醒醒 斯派洛
Wake up Sparrow.

889
01:19:46,540 --> 01:19:48,080
醒醒 斯派洛
Wake up, Sparrow.

890
01:19:48,580 --> 01:19:52,420
- 是时候还债了 - 猪哥
- It's time to pay your debt. - Pig?

891
01:19:53,250 --> 01:19:54,300
凯莉猪
Pig Kelly?

892
01:19:55,550 --> 01:19:58,510
- 我的老伙计 - 伙计
- Mi old mate. - Mate?

893
01:19:58,840 --> 01:20:00,510
孩子们听到没
Do you hear that boys?

894
01:20:01,140 --> 01:20:04,440
这个海盗欠我一大笔银子
This pirate owes me a blunder of silver.

895
01:20:04,520 --> 01:20:07,480
老天爷将他带到了刽子湾
And luck has brought him to Hangman's Bay.

896
01:20:07,560 --> 01:20:10,560
在这他能还清欠款 从此两清
Where he can settle his debt, here and now.

897
01:20:11,480 --> 01:20:14,530
我会的 猪哥 你说个数吧
And I will, I will Pig. Name your price.

898
01:20:14,610 --> 01:20:17,400
她叫碧翠丝
Her name is Beatrice.

899
01:20:20,370 --> 01:20:22,910
她是我可怜的寡妇妹妹
And she is my poor widowed sister.

900
01:20:25,750 --> 01:20:27,040
啊 那是什么玩意啊
What, what is that?

901
01:20:27,120 --> 01:20:29,040
她一直在找好男人
She's been looking for a respectable man.

902
01:20:30,000 --> 01:20:32,590
- 但你也勉强可以了 - 罗伊斯 赶紧开始吧
- But you'll have to do. - Royce, let's get on with this.

903
01:20:32,710 --> 01:20:34,460
不 为什么 为什么非？...
No why? Why?...

904
01:20:34,550 --> 01:20:37,050
让她做回女人 对她好 杰克
To make an honest woman of her, Jack.

905
01:20:37,130 --> 01:20:39,880
恭喜你 今天你要结婚了
Congratulations, it's your wedding day.

906
01:20:41,180 --> 01:20:42,100
可以开始了吗
Let us begin?

907
01:20:42,180 --> 01:20:44,970
我们会在谷仓中度蜜月
We will honeymoon in the barn.

908
01:20:49,350 --> 01:20:51,820
不 别这样 猪哥
No, no, no. Pig.

909
01:20:51,900 --> 01:20:55,070
我怎么可能真心实意地对它好呢
How can I honestly make an honest woman out of it?

910
01:20:55,150 --> 01:20:57,030
她 我的意思是她
That, her. I mean. Her.

911
01:21:00,740 --> 01:21:03,280
- 这玩意都是什么 - 我们的子嗣
- What are those things? - Our children.

912
01:21:03,910 --> 01:21:06,080
最好别和他们对视
Best not look them in the eye.

913
01:21:06,160 --> 01:21:08,330
带伴娘伴郎来
Bring the best man and the bridesmaid.

914
01:21:09,790 --> 01:21:11,090
我看它的眼睛了
I looked it in the eye.

915
01:21:11,170 --> 01:21:13,420
将手放在圣经上
Place your hand on the Bible.

916
01:21:14,250 --> 01:21:16,250
- 我有疥疮 - 巧了 我也有
- I have got scabies. - So do I.

917
01:21:17,260 --> 01:21:19,420
手放在圣经上
Place your hand on the Bible.

918
01:21:20,130 --> 01:21:21,430
我爱尿炕
I'm a bed wetter.

919
01:21:21,890 --> 01:21:23,300
说你愿意
Say I do.

920
01:21:24,390 --> 01:21:27,560
- 否则我爆了你的头 - 杰克 他们真要杀死我们
- Or I'll put a bullet in your skull. - Jack, they are going to kill us.

921
01:21:27,640 --> 01:21:29,230
- 我不在乎 - 快同意吧
- I don't care! - Just say I do.

922
01:21:29,310 --> 01:21:32,020
- 最后机会 - 等下 当然
- Last chance Jack. - Wait. Surely...

923
01:21:32,270 --> 01:21:34,860
- 这并不合法 - 不合法
- This is not legal. - This is not legal.

924
01:21:35,190 --> 01:21:36,320
他说得对
He's right.

925
01:21:36,400 --> 01:21:38,820
在场有人反对这桩婚姻吗？
Does any man here object to the nuptials?

926
01:21:39,400 --> 01:21:41,990
- 我 - 恭喜
- I do. - Congratulations.

927
01:21:42,070 --> 01:21:43,620
你可以亲吻新娘了
You may kiss the bride.

928
01:21:56,090 --> 01:21:59,210
你爱吃海鲜 对吧？
Do you like seafood, do you?

929
01:22:02,630 --> 01:22:04,930
杰克 又见面了
Jack. We meet again.

930
01:22:06,010 --> 01:22:07,140
赫克托
Hector!

931
01:22:07,430 --> 01:22:09,940
这是我全世界最好的朋友
This is mi best mate in the whole world.

932
01:22:10,020 --> 01:22:12,730
我一直知道你早晚会安心结婚
I always knew you'll settle down, eventually.

933
01:22:12,810 --> 01:22:14,190
你给我带礼物了吗
Did you bring me a gift?

934
01:22:16,480 --> 01:22:17,730
这样也行
That'll do.

935
01:22:20,110 --> 01:22:23,660
你看着很精神 脚步十分轻盈
You look marvelous. Got quite a spring in your step.

936
01:22:24,740 --> 01:22:26,070
你的腿长出来了吗
Has your leg grown back?

937
01:22:26,200 --> 01:22:28,540
船长 我们不该回去找萨拉查
Captain, shouldn't we be getting back to Salazar.

938
01:22:28,830 --> 01:22:31,200
用斯派洛先生的命换我们的吗？
Trade Mr. Sparrow's life in for our own?

939
01:22:31,500 --> 01:22:35,540
可以那么做 但我是来找波塞冬三叉戟的
I know that we could. But I've come for the Trident Poseidon.

940
01:22:36,500 --> 01:22:38,090
你要出卖那帮亡灵吗？
You're gonna double cross the dead?

941
01:22:38,170 --> 01:22:39,250
你向他们承诺过
You did promise!

942
01:22:39,460 --> 01:22:43,380
所以我会摧毁偷走我对大海控制权的亡灵
And with it I'll gut the dead that stole my command of the sea.

943
01:22:43,470 --> 01:22:45,550
虽然我很喜欢这个计划
As much as I love this plan.

944
01:22:45,800 --> 01:22:49,430
什么船都逃不脱那凄惨可悲的船的魔掌
No vessel can outrun that wretched haul of the ship.

945
01:22:49,510 --> 01:22:51,100
有的 杰克
But there be one, Jack.

946
01:22:51,180 --> 01:22:52,560
我见过的最快的船
The fastest ship I know.

947
01:22:52,640 --> 01:22:56,520
黑珍珠号 被困在黑胡子的瓶子里
The pearl, trapped in that bottle by Blackbeard.

948
01:22:56,600 --> 01:22:58,270
五个寒冬前
Five winters ago.

949
01:23:00,150 --> 01:23:03,190
以强盗至高无上的剑起誓
By the power of that blaggerd sovereign blade...

950
01:23:03,280 --> 01:23:08,780
我在此返还黑珍珠号曾经应得的荣耀
I hereby release the Black Pearl, to her former and rightful glory.

951
01:23:19,750 --> 01:23:21,050
弄掉那
Get rid of the...

952
01:23:23,840 --> 01:23:24,550
要来了
It's coming.

953
01:23:24,630 --> 01:23:26,550
它要出现了 来了来了
It is coming! It is coming! Coming!

954
01:23:31,560 --> 01:23:33,980
放一边
Set aside.

955
01:23:35,480 --> 01:23:36,900
要来了
It's coming!

956
01:23:52,580 --> 01:23:54,080
缩水了
It's shrunken.

957
01:23:54,700 --> 01:23:56,370
为什么不能恢复原样呢
Why doesn't it unshrink?

958
01:23:57,370 --> 01:23:58,960
也许天太冷了
Maybe it's cold.

959
01:23:59,080 --> 01:24:00,630
她要回到海上
She needs the sea.

960
01:24:14,930 --> 01:24:16,560
她曾经是艘好船
She was a fine ship.

961
01:24:55,140 --> 01:24:57,770
船上只需要一位船长
There be room for only one captain.

962
01:25:00,400 --> 01:25:03,980
- 肮脏的畜生 - 该去与亡灵赛跑了
- Filthy beast. - Time to race the dead.

963
01:25:10,780 --> 01:25:12,990
唯一安全的地方就是陆地
The only safe place is the land.

964
01:25:13,120 --> 01:25:14,910
为什么我们要离开陆地
Why are we going away from the land?

965
01:25:15,370 --> 01:25:16,370
没人知道吗
Nobody knows?

966
01:25:16,910 --> 01:25:19,290
船长 你的地图不完整
Captain, your map is incomplete.

967
01:25:19,580 --> 01:25:22,330
如果你相信我 我能带大家去找三叉戟
I can take us to the Trident, if you'd only trust me.

968
01:25:23,330 --> 01:25:25,500
你听我刚才说的了吗
Did you not hear anything I just said?

969
01:25:25,880 --> 01:25:27,010
所以你的意思是
So you be saying.

970
01:25:27,090 --> 01:25:29,590
那颗星星假装自己是地图吗
Is that star pretending to be a map?

971
01:25:29,760 --> 01:25:32,140
船长 任何地图上都没有陆地
Sir, there is no island, on any map,

972
01:25:32,220 --> 01:25:34,100
那女人说的毫无根据
to support what the woman says.

973
01:25:34,180 --> 01:25:36,010
船长 你不用理解她说的话
Captain, you don't have to understand her.

974
01:25:36,180 --> 01:25:37,640
只需要相信她
Just believe her.

975
01:25:38,770 --> 01:25:40,190
有人吗？
Any one?

976
01:25:52,280 --> 01:25:55,660
要是有锋利的东西 我就能撬锁
We had something sharp, I could pick that lock.

977
01:25:57,040 --> 01:25:59,040
在这里你绝对找不到锋利的玩意
You are not gonna find anything sharp in here.

978
01:26:21,430 --> 01:26:22,480
放了他们
Release them.

979
01:26:24,730 --> 01:26:29,110
船长 你不会想让女人掌舵吧
Sir, you wouldn't allow a woman to steer your ship?

980
01:26:29,190 --> 01:26:32,400
让她去追星星 否则我们都会死
She will follow her star. Or we'll all die together.

981
01:26:52,050 --> 01:26:55,010
黑珍珠号 又起航了
The Black Pearl. She sails again.

982
01:26:58,140 --> 01:27:00,770
这艘船 那些鬼
This ship. Those ghosts.

983
01:27:01,770 --> 01:27:03,520
都无法用常理来解释
There can be no logical explanation.

984
01:27:03,600 --> 01:27:05,650
海之传说是真的 卡丽娜
Myths of the sea are real, Carina.

985
01:27:05,980 --> 01:27:08,020
很高兴你终于能意识到自己想错了
I'm glad you can finally see you were wrong.

986
01:27:08,150 --> 01:27:09,150
错
Wrong?

987
01:27:11,280 --> 01:27:12,570
也许我确实怀疑过
Perhaps I had some doubts.

988
01:27:12,650 --> 01:27:14,530
这是我听过最糟的道歉了
This is the worst apology I've ever heard.

989
01:27:14,610 --> 01:27:16,360
道歉 我为什么要道歉
Apology? Why would I apologize?

990
01:27:16,450 --> 01:27:18,620
因为我们在被亡灵追捕 开一艘
Because we've been chased by the dead, sailing on a ship,

991
01:27:18,700 --> 01:27:20,870
从瓶子里蹦出的船 科学如何解释
raised from a bottle. Where is your science in that?

992
01:27:20,950 --> 01:27:23,370
好吧 我会道歉
Fine, I will apologize.

993
01:27:24,080 --> 01:27:24,830
接着说
Go on, then.

994
01:27:25,040 --> 01:27:26,920
那样的话 你可能也要和我道歉
Well then, one could argue that you owe me an apology.

995
01:27:27,000 --> 01:27:29,710
我的生命因为你被海盗与亡灵威胁
As my life has been threatened by pirates and dead man.

996
01:27:29,790 --> 01:27:31,960
现在你相信了 虽然这么说很欠打
Which you now believe in, sorry to say.

997
01:27:32,300 --> 01:27:33,550
我原谅你
Apology accepted.

998
01:27:35,680 --> 01:27:37,140
我去望风
I am going to the lookout.

999
01:27:37,720 --> 01:27:39,430
很高兴你这么想
I'm glad you see it my way!

1000
01:27:48,980 --> 01:27:51,650
- 准备好枪 - 准备好枪
- Ready the guns. - Aye. Ready the guns!

1001
01:27:51,730 --> 01:27:53,820
这些海盗是冲着三叉戟来的
These pirates are going for the trident.

1002
01:28:08,500 --> 01:28:10,630
这你是从哪拿到的 姑娘
Where did you get that from Missy?

1003
01:28:11,290 --> 01:28:14,380
我知道这本书 十多年前
I know this book, stolen from an Italian ship,

1004
01:28:14,460 --> 01:28:16,630
- 从意大利船上偷的 - 偷
- many years ago. - Stolen?

1005
01:28:17,010 --> 01:28:18,260
不 你看认错了
No, you're mistaken.

1006
01:28:18,340 --> 01:28:20,140
书封皮上本有一颗红宝石
There was a Ruby on the cover...

1007
01:28:20,220 --> 01:28:22,260
非常记忆犹新
I would not soon forget.

1008
01:28:25,480 --> 01:28:27,360
这是我父亲给我的
This was given to me by my father.

1009
01:28:27,440 --> 01:28:29,560
他明明是个科学家
He was clearly a man of science.

1010
01:28:31,560 --> 01:28:33,690
显然他是个小偷
He was clearly a common thief.

1011
01:28:35,110 --> 01:28:37,030
我对父亲的回忆
The memory of my father will not be befouled...

1012
01:28:37,110 --> 01:28:38,660
才不会被海盗之舌玷污
by the tongue of a pirate.

1013
01:28:39,360 --> 01:28:41,200
这本日记是我生来就有的
This diary is my birth right.

1014
01:28:41,570 --> 01:28:43,740
被放在儿童之家的台阶上
Left to me on the steps of a children's home.

1015
01:28:44,330 --> 01:28:46,080
还留了一个名字 仅此而已
Along with a name and nothing else.

1016
01:28:46,370 --> 01:28:48,160
所以你是孤儿咯
Oh, so you are an orphan?

1017
01:28:49,210 --> 01:28:50,630
你叫什么
What be you called?

1018
01:28:52,790 --> 01:28:55,050
北方的明亮之星赋予我名字
Brightest star in the North gave me my name.

1019
01:29:01,850 --> 01:29:05,100
- 所以你叫卡丽娜 - 卡丽娜·史密斯
- That would be Carina? - Carina Smyth.

1020
01:29:06,980 --> 01:29:11,100
- 你确实很了解星象 - 我是船长
- So, you do know your stars? - I'm a captain.

1021
01:29:14,570 --> 01:29:17,400
我知道跟着哪颗星星能回家
I know which stars to follow home.

1022
01:30:00,530 --> 01:30:01,860
史密斯
Smyth?

1023
01:30:02,860 --> 01:30:05,330
史密斯十个不同寻常的姓
Smyth is quite an unusual name.

1024
01:30:06,530 --> 01:30:10,080
我们不也认识一位吗 老史密斯
Did we not once know someone, old Smyth?

1025
01:30:10,160 --> 01:30:11,460
别捣乱
Shut your trip.

1026
01:30:11,580 --> 01:30:13,080
她叫什么来着
What was her name.

1027
01:30:13,670 --> 01:30:15,460
到嘴边了就是想不出
It's right on the tip of mi tongue...

1028
01:30:15,840 --> 01:30:17,590
你想丢掉舌头吗
Do you wanna loose that tongue?

1029
01:30:17,670 --> 01:30:18,760
玛格丽特·史密斯
Margaret Smyth.

1030
01:30:20,260 --> 01:30:22,380
我们达成一致了吗
Aye, so we making accord then?

1031
01:30:22,800 --> 01:30:25,300
还是我去告诉那个人
Or, Shall I tell you know who...

1032
01:30:25,760 --> 01:30:27,850
我们都知道真相
What we both know it's the truth.

1033
01:30:27,930 --> 01:30:30,400
你我要把这个秘密带入坟墓
We both take the secret to our grave.

1034
01:30:30,480 --> 01:30:32,270
所以是真的咯 我只是在虚张声势
You mean, it is true? I was bluffing.

1035
01:30:32,350 --> 01:30:33,150
才不是
I am not!

1036
01:30:33,230 --> 01:30:36,520
杀了我 你就没东西给亡灵了
You kill me, you got nothing to bow to the deadness.

1037
01:30:36,980 --> 01:30:38,780
你需要我
So you need me.

1038
01:30:39,860 --> 01:30:44,580
必须坦白 赫克托 你真的非常非常丑
I will have to frank Hector. You are very, very ugly.

1039
01:30:44,660 --> 01:30:48,990
你怎么会生出那么位可人呢？
So how could you produce a fetching creature such as that?

1040
01:30:49,600 --> 01:30:51,200
玛格丽特死了
Margaret died.

1041
01:30:51,600 --> 01:30:54,370
我尽了一个不成器的强盗最大的努力
That worthless blaggerd ever could.

1042
01:30:54,370 --> 01:30:54,750


1043
01:30:54,750 --> 01:30:58,340
我把还是婴儿的她送进孤儿院 不曾回去看她
I placed the infant in an orphanage, never to see her again.

1044
01:30:58,590 --> 01:31:01,340
我以为留下红宝石可以让她过得好一点
I thought the ruby might afford her some easy life...

1045
01:31:01,420 --> 01:31:03,880
没想到她会去研究那本日记
But I never imagined she would take those scribblings...

1046
01:31:04,130 --> 01:31:05,720
想要解开身世之谜
Make a life of her own.

1047
01:31:07,010 --> 01:31:09,140
还是回到了我身边
Life that's led her back to me.

